pasta.domain.template

Class UnitTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • pasta.domain.template.UnitTest

  • public class UnitTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Container class for a unit test. Contains the name of the unit test and whether it has been tested. String representation: 
    <unitTestProperties>
        <name>name</name>
        <tested>true|false</tested>
</unitTestProperties>

    File location on disk: $projectLocation$/template/unitTest/$unitTestName$

    Since:
    2012-11-13
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Alex Radu
